there are so many other factors to consider.<br>
<br>
1) nearly all high end druids are spec alteration, moonfire is an evocation spell. primary and secondary spec is a mana savings difference of roughly 10%. so, add 400 mana to the druids cost.<br>
<br>
2) wizards have an innate class reduction to nuke resists and hate, druids do not. <br>
<br>
3) wizards have superior mana regeneration.<br>
<br>
